snippet.title: Blast Rush - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Blasting is everything in Blast Rush, the infinite-bomb shoot-em-up for mobile from Bipedal Dog.

Download on the App Store for iPad and iPhone:
http://bit.ly/blastrush-ios

For Android on Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.bipedaldog.bak

And the Amazon Appstore:
https://www.amazon.com/dp/B079QZ93B1

http://blastrush.com
http://bipedal.dog

TWITTER: @bipedaldog
